<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ881007-0185 </DOCNO><HL> International -- Corporate Report: Ariadne Australia Ltd. </HL><SO>  </SO><IN> ERN SCR </IN><TEXT>   Ariadne Australia Ltd., an investment concern hit hard by last October's stockmarket crash, reported an operating loss after tax of 640 million Australian dollars (US$507.9 million) for the year ended June 30.    In the previous fiscal year Ariadne had operating profit of A$142.2 million.    Sales rose 33%, to A$1.57 billion from A$1.18 billion, while other revenue increased by more than six times, to A$78 million from A$12 million. </TEXT></DOC>